Test Case ID: TC-002

Title:
Verify user can add multiple items to the cart

Priority:
High

Type:
Functional (Positive)

Preconditions:
1. User is successfully signed in.
2. User in on the Products page.

Test Steps:
1. Choose multiple different items and click the Add to Cart button

Expected Result
1. All selected items are added to the cart.
2. The cart badge displays the correct number of items.
3. Each selected item's button changes to Remove.
